<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<title>로그인 - GS Retail</title>
	<meta name="viewport" content="user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, width=device-width, target-densitydpi=medium-dpi" />
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,address=no,email=no" />
	<meta name="description" contents=""/>
	<meta name="keywords" contents=""/>
	<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="../images/favicon/favicon.ico">
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="../images/favicon/favicon.png">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/common.css">
	<script src="../../js/jquery-1.12.4.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../../js/plugin.js"></script>
	<script src="../../js/common.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
	<div class="skipMenu"><a href="#container">본문 바로가기</a></div>
	<div class="wrapper">
		<header class="header">
			<h1>설정</h1>
			<a href="#" class="btnBack">이전 페이지 이동</a>
		</header>
		<!-- //header -->
		<section id="container" class="content">
            <!-- 내용 -->
			<div class="settingArea line">
				<div class="logInfo">
					<p><em class="color02">텍스트 텍스트 텍스트</em>님 환영합니다.</p>
					<a href="#" role="button" class="btnTS btnS">로그아웃</a>
				</div>
				<a href="#" class="pushLink">내 정보</a>
				<div class="eventPush">
					<div class="infoPush">
						<strong>이벤트 및 혜택 알림</strong>
						<p class="subTxt">GS리테일에서 제공하는 행사/이벤트, 상품의 유효기간, 선물내역 등 다양한 혜택 안내를 받으실 수 있습니다.</p>
						<span class="tgSwich">
							<input type="checkbox" id="select01"><!-- id값과 label의 for값 동일하여야 함 -->
							<label for="select01"></label>
						</span>
					</div>
					<div class="pushList"><!-- 더보기 활성화시에 class값 on 추가 -->
						<ul>
							<li>
								<strong>THE POP</strong>
								<span class="tgSwich">
									<input type="checkbox" id="eventPush01">
									<label for="eventPush01"></label>
								</span>
							</li>
							<li>
								<strong>GS25</strong>
								<span class="tgSwich">
									<input type="checkbox" id="eventPush02">
									<label for="eventPush02"></label>
								</span>
							</li>
							<li>
								<strong>GS THE FRESH</strong>
								<span class="tgSwich">
									<input type="checkbox" id="eventPush02">
									<label for="eventPush02"></label>
								</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
						<a href="#" role="button" class="btnTS btnS">알림 확인</a>
					</div>
					<button type="button" aria-selected="false" class="btnMore type02">더보기</button><!-- 선택되었을시 aria값 true -->
				</div>
				<div class="regularStore">
					<strong>단골매장 설정</strong>
					<ul>
						<li>
							<a href="#">
								<img src="../../image/common/img_regular_storeGS25.jpg" alt="GS25">
								<em>도곡렉슬점</em>
							</a>
						</li>
						<li>
							<a href="#">
								<img src="../../image/common/img_regular_storeGSFRESH.jpg" alt="GS THE FRESH">
								<em>도곡렉슬점</em>
							</a>
						</li>
						<li>
							<a href="#">
								<img src="../../image/common/img_regular_storelala.jpg" alt="GS THE FRESH">
								<em>도곡렉슬점</em>
							</a>
						</li>
					</ul>
					<a href="#" role="button" class="linkBtn">단골 최근이용 보기</a>
				</div>

				<div class="regularStore">
					<strong>단골매장 설정</strong>
					<p class="noData">등록된 단골매장이 없습니다.</p>
					<a href="#" role="button" class="linkBtn">단골 최근이용 보기</a>
				</div>

				<a href="#" class="pushLink">
					현금영수증 발급 설정<em>010-6848-2000</em>
				</a>

				<a href="#" class="pushLink">
					현금영수증 발급 설정<em>등록된 현금영수증 발급 정보가 없습니다.</em>
				</a>


			</div>
            <!--//내용 -->
		</section>
		<!-- //container -->
	</div>
	<!-- //wrapper -->
</body>
</html>

